description:
Mollie Hemingway, senior editor at The Federalist and author of "Rigged: How the Media, Big Tech, and the Democrats Seized Our Elections," joins C&B to discuss Biden's phony "voting rights" push and Kavanaugh joining the libs on the health care worker vax mandate. Do masks make liberals more attractive to other liberals? Is Russia about to roll into Ukraine? C&B take calls.
